name: Nathaniel's Basics Series Part 5
description:
I'm glad this is almost over the content gets increasingly depressive.

Oh no! The end of the Nathan's Basics universe as we know it?? Maybe! And also a big secret is revealed. See if you can stop the evil people from ending your least favourite world! 

(Hint: go back to the menu and reselect the map for the item names to change)
